content: #尊酷元旦风俗#【西班牙：争着吃葡萄】在西班牙，当除夕夜12点的钟声刚开始敲第一声，人们便争着吃葡萄，如果能按钟声的节奏吃下12颗，便象征着新年的每个月都平安如意。新年葡萄的每颗还有不同的含意，分别代表“平安”、“和睦”、“避难”、“祛病”等。
content_translated: In Spain, when the clock at 12 o'clock on New Year's Eve begins to ring first, people fight to eat grapes, and if they eat 12 of them at the bell's pace, it symbolizes every month of the New Year. Each grape of the New Year's grapes also has different meanings, namely “peace”, “peace”, “peace”, “asylum”, “sickness”.

content: #尊酷元旦风俗#【比利时：给牲畜拜年】比利时的新年动物最受宠。元旦这天，比利时人清早起床后做的第一件事是给动物们拜年。他们会走到牛、羊以及自己的宠物猫宠物狗身边，煞有介事地向它们问候：“新年快乐！”
content_translated: The new year's animals in Belgium are the favorite. On New Year's Day, the first thing the Belgians do when they wake up early in the morning is to celebrate the animals. They'll go to the cows, the sheep and their own pet cats and dogs, and greet them in good faith: "Happy New Year!"

content: 按照中国官方的固有思维，民众示威游行是对现体制的挑战，有损社会主义国家形象，花都事例反映出广东“维稳”思维出现关键转折。与原来信奉“刚性维稳”相比，广东正探索“弹性稳定”的可能，即存在公民博弈，有公开利益抗争的稳定。政府不直接介入纠纷，而是扮演秩序维护者的角色。
content_translated: According to China's official thinking, popular demonstrations are a challenge to the current system and undermine the image of the socialist State, and the example of flowers reflects a critical shift in Guangdong's “stable” thinking. Compared to the original belief in “resistence and security”, Guangdong is exploring the possibility of “flexible stability”, i.e. the existence of civic games and the stability of overt interests. The Government was not directly involved in the dispute, but rather acted as the guardian of order.

content: 广东再次成为自由派知识分子寄予希望的改革开放排头兵。此时，广东的改革精神不是体现在开辟经济特区的勇气，不是大踏步加速市场化改革，也不是“腾笼换鸟”的决心，而是推进较深层次的行政与社会体制改革。
content_translated: Guangdong has once again become a leader in the reform that liberal intellectuals have hoped for. At this time, the spirit of reform in Guangdong is not reflected in the courage to open up the Special Economic Zone, nor in the determination to accelerate market-based reform, nor to “scramble for birds”, but rather in the advancement of deeper administrative and social institutional reforms.

content: 这款生态概念车就是专为那些喜欢外出郊游的年轻人设计的。它的车身采用铝制仿生镂空结构，整车重量非常轻，不仅节约能源，行驶起来还十分灵活。车上特殊玻璃制成的车门可以像蝴蝶翅膀一样展开，并能通过用户控制，变换车门的颜色和透明度，保护用户的隐私安全。

Its body is aluminum-based emptiness, and its overall weight is very light, not only saving energy, but also operating with great flexibility. Car doors made of special glass can operate like butterflies' wings, and can change the colour and transparency of the doors through user control and protect the privacy of users.

content: 简单来说，这是一款可以自己拼装的座椅，一共由三部分组成：支架，坐垫和靠背，组装起来非常简单容易。不仅如此，它还有优美的曲线外形，设计师将这部作品起名为：Sputnik Chear，将它与卫星一样比喻。的确如此，简单的设计，超高的易用性，再加上独特的外形品味，使它更加像一款非常实用的艺术品。
content_translated: In short, it is a seat that can be assembled on its own. It consists of three parts: a stand, a cushion and a back, which is very simple to assemble. Not only that, but it also has a beautiful curvature, and the designer named it Sputnik Chir, like a satellite. Indeed, simple design, super easy to use, with unique appearances, makes it more like a very practical work of art.

content: 最犯賤的女人，就是跟有愛侶的男人上床的女人。最噁心的女人，就是明明別人有愛侶還要粘上去的女人。最沒用的女人，就是用眼淚來挽留男人的女人。最白痴的女人，就是有第三者出現就放手的女人。最好的女人，就是在你一無所有的時候還一直陪伴你只愛你一個的女人。

The most useless woman is the woman who uses tears to hold men back. The stupidest woman is a woman who let go when a third person shows up. The best woman is a woman who's always been with you when you had nothing.

content: 【智慧语录】1、男人的帅不在脸蛋，而在于岁月积淀下来的睿智与淡定。2、把想做的事、必做的事当成乐趣来做；可做可不做的事情等有兴致再做。3、教育的目的是为了帮助人们在未来的生活中更成功地寻找自己的幸福。4、先为成功的人工作，再与成功的人合作，最后是让成功的人为你工作。
content_translated: One, a man's handsomeness is not in his face, but in the wisdom and calmness of his years. 2. Do what you want, what you have to do as fun; do what you can and don't; do what you can. 3. Education aims to help people find their own happiness more successfully in their future lives. 4. Work for the successful, then work with the successful, and finally let the successful work for you.

content: 女人越吃越年轻自信的10种食物:①新鲜乳酪——抢救记忆力；②金枪鱼——PK脂肪；③蜂蜜——净化血液；④橙子——增强免疫力；⑤绿菜花——年轻心脏；⑥鸡蛋——呵护乳房；⑦燕麦片——降低胆固醇；⑧花生酱——永葆青春；⑨咖啡——食物催情；⑩巧克力——走出情绪低谷。
content_translated: The younger women eat the more confident 10 foods: 1 fresh cheese — memory rescue; 2 tuna — PK fat; 3 honey — blood purification; 4 oranges — enhanced immunity; 5 green vegetables — young heart; 6 eggs — breast care; 7 oatmeals — reduced cholesterol; 8 peanut butter — eternal youth; 9 coffee — food rush; 10 chocolate — out of mood.

content: 一直觉得妥协一些、将就一些、容忍一些可以得到幸福，但当你的底线放得越低，你得到的就是更低的结果。不要总抱怨自己遇到的人都不靠谱，如果别人总这么对你，那么一定是你教会了别人用这样的方式对你。 爱是平等的，可以付出更多，也可以爱他更多，但决不是妥协、将就、容忍。
content_translated: There has always been a feeling of compromise, of tolerance, of happiness, but when your bottom line is lower, you get lower results. Don't always complain about the people you meet. If people do that to you, you must have taught people how to treat you. Love is equal and can give or love him more, but it is not compromise, will, tolerance.

content: 【语录】出生一张纸，开始一辈子；毕业一张纸，奋斗一辈子；婚姻一张纸，折磨一辈子；做官一张纸, 斗争一辈子；金钱一张纸，辛苦一辈子；荣誉一张纸，虚名一辈子；看病一张纸，痛苦一辈子；悼词一张纸，了结一辈子；淡化这些纸，明白一辈子；忘了这些纸，快乐一辈子。
content_translated: Born a piece of paper, starting a lifetime; graduated a piece of paper, fighting for a lifetime; married a piece of paper, tormenting a lifetime; fought a lifetime, fighting for a lifetime; spent a lifetime of money, working hard for a lifetime; spent a lifetime of honour, having a false name; spent a lifetime of pain, seeing a single piece of paper; ended a lifetime of eulogy; reduced those pieces of paper, understanding a lifetime; forgotten them, happy life.

content: 【对于生活】我们应该从容的面对与接受，无论结果是获得还是失去。很多时候我们会觉得前路茫茫不知道路在何方。其实路一直就在脚下，一切的过去都是以现在为归宿，一切的未来都是以现在为起点！不管过去多么暗淡，也不管未来多么辉煌，往前走吧！正如，我们不应害怕生命会结束，而应担心它从未开始！
content_translated: [For life] We should face and accept, whether the result is acquisition or loss. Many times we feel that we don't know where we are. In fact, the road has always been at its feet, and the past is now, and the future is now! No matter how dark the past may be, no matter how bright the future may be, go ahead! Just as we should not fear that life will end, but that it will never begin!

content: 新年之际，这帮孙子成群结队出洞挣工分。做老大的也太抠门了，一个帖子才￥0.50元，物价这么高,它们又没日没夜地加班，这大过年的,还得延时加班，就凭这半元半元地挣，啥时候能发家致富？真替这帮舔菊的家伙着急。强烈呼吁给0.50元们加工资，让它们能安心忠于主子，卖力干活，情绪稳定。
content_translated: On the occasion of the New Year, the grandkids came out in groups to earn their jobs. It's too cheap to be a boss. It's only $0.50 for a post, it's so expensive, they work day and night. It's too late, it's too late. I'm so worried about these ass-lickers. A strong appeal was made for a salary increase of $0.50 to enable them to remain loyal to their masters, to work hard and to be emotionally stable.
